      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/582461055_18106967680609681_5507458579997012247_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=103&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzc2NjM3NjM4NDI2NDk2MTM5NA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=Q59rx3D-q4wQ7kNvwHJyyQM&amp;_nc_oc=Ado9vGeSGDS_71ouIk-VzdBT0aZoYQkoY0Uk3rZ3GoY8KmKZ8wTwkXcL33BMRcBUX_4&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=GZgQIv5tM4-CD8gju3XUTA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzaJXCeqoSspdBRHdBuYuMaxB_8zMwadzUUS_TOiWdwbg&amp;oe=69CA32BE" alt="Slide 1 fra @theunseenalchemist" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/582920772_18106967677609681_2773522964442248236_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=104&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzc2NjM3NjM4NDIyMzA1MDc5Mg%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=nzaLzreKwzAQ7kNvwGtkeyr&amp;_nc_oc=AdqOXiZuelRUAjZUDYrwYmETFkYiI8Zebj6tIzvcPT3_m-zQxeSHNAtQK0uVqYrBQiE&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=GZgQIv5tM4-CD8gju3XUTA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afxe58BrWO-wMiqNxu_sfwRQMvJ_DtpdgY3rrVp2X3wMEA&amp;oe=69CA231C" alt="Slide 2 fra @theunseenalchemist" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/581614179_18106967698609681_3432341986880456887_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=111&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzc2NjM3NjM4MzQ2ODA3NDExOA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=STwC4uuq2X8Q7kNvwEURAtG&amp;_nc_oc=AdqC6Ql9arrcfeYqBSpOFRBe9hi1kk37wtUV0GMyzSkeHUzk4ZesFpBRB1xlkhSSKco&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=GZgQIv5tM4-CD8gju3XUTA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwuN7E4l3NnC1NKOwTCqc5WrUuBQP5tcaF2kAaaFQzl2Q&amp;oe=69CA3E10" alt="Slide 3 fra @theunseenalchemist" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/582535977_18106967695609681_2918083499098188995_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=107&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzc2NjM3NjM4NDI2NDkzMDEyMA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwODB4MTA4MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=KUk3wZasBmkQ7kNvwGGAfeg&amp;_nc_oc=AdouOpQer7uoD-TVjIrRXiTZTeYyCg0dBV9KSso0l9a30sSfiGthtzQI0YoIP4Ll5QA&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=GZgQIv5tM4-CD8gju3XUTA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwaR5Q4cpIw4IG0H9WjArwUYKnukAPWQ_F0XF7QTeuMIA&amp;oe=69CA2296" alt="Slide 4 fra @theunseenalchemist" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /></p><p><strong>🖼️ Slideshow (4 medier)</strong></p><p><strong>@theunseenalchemist</strong></p><p>Have you ever seen a cats eye reflect in 800mm macro lens? <br/>
<br/>
The glow of light inside a cats eye is caused by light bouncing off the tapetum lucidum, a layer of crystal - containing cells located behind the retina. <br/>
<br/>
2 years ago I was honoured to sit patiently alongside @timflachphotography and my gorgeous Devon Rex cat @gobbolinothewitchescat to try to capture a reflective cats eye under macro lens for the first time. <br/>
<br/>
Using some tips from shooting reflective materials I’d picked up along the way with @theunseenbeauty and Tim’s incredible experience after 3 days the shot was caught! <br/>
<br/>
A 100mm lens wasn’t viable, as the reflection required atleast 3m of distance, instead Tim flew in a rare canon 800mm RF lens, with additional close up rings and a high speed broncolor ring flash to ignite the reflection. <br/>
<br/>
Included as part of the wonderful new book Feline out now! <br/>
<br/>
Well done Gobbi for staying still (eventually) <br/>
<br/>
#cat #catseye #timflach #catphoto #catlover #macro #caturday #photographer #nature #naturephotography #animalphotography</p><p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DRE22IciCXH/">Se slideshow på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
