      <title>Aerodynamic makeup, another crystal based recipe - this time a diff colour tuned...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DNRBj_doVFd/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DNRBj_doVFd/"><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/530726613_18098076118609681_3594290341544752607_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s640x640_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=102&amp;ig_cache_key=MzY5Nzc0MzY0MDQxODkzMTAzNw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjcyMHgxMjgwLnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=KyMH-4gCeW4Q7kNvwEgxzS6&amp;_nc_oc=Adob7rHIgxIujkDkQyVbBwfrC9f03SKUdbMV8FvkCLEkEWX0TQOUhm1f8pKkx9nnrp8&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=GZgQIv5tM4-CD8gju3XUTA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwMFhAwfbXejzyj3kdPM4GeiyN3amEtdQ35Oins4ho1lQ&amp;oe=69CA2A11" alt="Video-thumbnail fra @theunseenalchemist" /></a></p><p><strong>🎬 Video</strong></p><p><strong>@theunseenalchemist</strong></p><p>Aerodynamic makeup, another crystal based recipe - this time a diff colour tuned to change on response to wind and air flow. I originally made this one for Formula One R&amp;D to track aerodynamics on the surface of the car then did one for humans too - Just to keep you amused while I sort out more heart beat makeup in the lab 🧪 <br/>
<br/>
AND YES ITS IRL not AI <br/>
<br/>
Ps the heartbeat arcane refs made me lols so this one’s for them! <br/>
Also loved OCTARINE for a potential collection name @theunseenbeauty <br/>
